citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:05-11:35am on
07-JUN-22. Inspector arrived at 11:05am, called the number on file with no answer, voicemail not set up to leave
message. Inspector knocked on door with no answer. Inspector waited 30 minutes, until 11:35am and then called again
with no answer. Flyer with note and buisness card left at door. Inspector then left site.
End Section
